@Superllama12 : Heh, nice comparison. And yeah, I also think this card is good, not a lot of one-drops become potentially big enough to become serious threats for your opponents...not at common at least (except for the quoted [Delver of Secrets](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Delver of Secrets) of course).  
-  
And yes, as a lot of Evolve cards, this is ideal "on the curve", but not good afterwards. But hey, simic has some ways to distribute counters. Plus, it's not as if this particular flaw is only present in creatures with Evolve...
